  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="home-info-header text-center"> How does it work? </h2>
<div class="home-info-container d-flex align-content-center justify-content-center">
  <div class="home-info-card">
    <div class="home-info-segment">
      <%= image_tag asset_path("t-d.svg") %>
      <p class="fs-4 mt-4"> Simply tell us where you want to go, and how long for. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-info-segment middle-segment-borders">
        <%= image_tag asset_path("m-d.svg") %>
        <p class="fs-4 mt-4"> We generate a route, including where to stay and what to do. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-info-segment">
      <%= image_tag asset_path("a-d.svg") %>
      <p class="fs-4 mt-4"> Fine tune to your heart's content, then set off on your adventure!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

